                  <div class="mini_text_title colour_white_text">11.What Rights Do You Have?</div>
                  <div>11.1 If the legal requirements are met: To ask us for access to your personal information, to rectify it if there are mistakes, to delete or restrict or object to its use in certain circumstances or to “data portability”.</div><br/>
